No. 10-7807. Khalid Awan, Petitioner v. United States. 562 U.S. 1170, 131 S. Ct. 969,

178 L. Ed. 2d 806,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 567. January 10, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Same case below, 607 F.3d 306 and 384 Fed. Appx. 9.
